text: Moominiinih yan maray Yallih gital sinni maalu yaceeh ceelallo meqe Burta-le Baaxol yubquren Amboytay malcina Sumbulti kak yawqeeh yaabukey kulli Sumbulti kak Bool Amboyta kak yakkeh inna, Yalli isih faxa marah galto dirribisah usuk Yallih fooca edde faxek, Yallih muxxo farakka leeh usuk isi naqoosah Niyaayit tanim yaaxigi kinni
